title: Garnish My Wages!  | Sal Vulcano & Chris Distefano Present: Hey Babe! | EP 49
description:
Hey Babe! is a podcast where comedians Chris Distefano and Sal Vulcano share stories and have fun. Let your hair down & come hang out with the BABES!
THE BABES are READY TO PARTY THIS THURSDAY! YASSSS! Chris' GF looks like Michael Jackson. Who has had more iconic looks than Michael Jackson?! What do the babes think of Michael Jackson. Chris asks for a friend about how to go to jail for tax evasion......what is tax evasion? Will Chris be going to jail?!?! Superman's son Jon Kent is Bi-Sexual. What is difference between bisexual and pansexual? Shout out Irish school nurses. Sal talks about a failed pilot he shot with the jokers. We watch back security footage of Chris falling on his face. What was life before GPS and google maps?!! AAA wtf is that?!?! A few stories from the pumpkin patch. What is a pumpkin? Someone pulled a mean prank on Sal.....WOW. Shout out  @TheHomelessPimp   for having INSANE & WEIRD style yasssss gurl! Make sure you see the babes performing in your city!!!
Rate us on iTunes!
